docs.lead_paragraph: Harrison Noel, 20 years old, son of a New York attorney, and once an asylum inmate, broke down late yesterday in the Montclair (N.J.) police headquarters and confessed that he had kidnapped and then murdered Mary Daly, 6 years old, last Friday.

headline.main: HE WAS ONCE IN ASYLUM; Harrison Noel Tells of Shooting Montclair Child of 6. EXAMINED FOR 23 HOURS Leads Police to Body, Then Admits Murder of Negro Chauffeur, Too. FACES 4 CRIMINAL CHARGES Says He Sought Ransom and Acknowledges He Made Telephone Demand for $4,000.

docs.snippet: Harrison Noel, 20 years old, son of a New York attorney, and once an asylum inmate, broke down late yesterday in the Montclair (N.J.) police headquarters and confessed that he had kidnapped and then murdered Mary Daly, 6 years old, last Friday.
